# 🎓 Student Portal Demo

This is a demo project for building a **Student Portal Application**, designed for educational institutions such as colleges, universities, or schools. The application allows students to access academic resources and administrative services from a centralized platform.

## 🚀 Features (Planned)

- 🧑‍🎓 Student Login & Registration
- 📚 View Academic Records (Grades, GPA, Transcripts)
- 📝 Course Enrollment & Schedule Management
- 🧾 Tuition Fee Payment & History
- 📅 Exam Timetable & Notifications
- 🧑‍🏫 Faculty Directory & Messaging
- 📁 Assignment Uploads & Document Downloads
- ✅ Attendance Tracking

## 🧰 Tech Stack (Proposal)

- **Frontend**: React.js / Next.js
- **Backend**: Node.js (Express) / Django
- **Database**: PostgreSQL / MongoDB
- **Authentication**: JWT / OAuth 2.0
- **Hosting**: Vercel / Netlify (Frontend), Heroku / Render / Railway (Backend)

## 📌 Purpose

This repository is for educational and demonstration purposes. It can be used as a foundation for developing real-world student portal systems or for learning full-stack web development.

---

Feel free to contribute, fork, or use the code as a starting point for your own student portal system!

